name: Filipino Jeepney
prompt: A VibeDeck controller decorated like a Filipino Jeepney. Chrome everything - chrome horse hood ornaments, chrome trim, chrome buttons. Explosive colors - hot pink, electric blue, yellow, orange. Hand-painted flowers, eagles, and religious imagery. Disco ball reflections. Maximum decoration, no empty space. The LCD has decorative frame. Tassels and ornaments hanging. Festive, loud, proud, uniquely Filipino. Bright tropical lighting.
why: Celebration of Filipino culture, maximalist joy
